title: Ep 24 - The Five Regrets of the Dying
itunes:title: Ep 24 - The Five Regrets of the Dying
description:
In this episode we dive into the book "The Five Regrets of the Dying." We speak about each regret and what we can learn from each in order to make sure we don't look back and have any regrets when our time finally comes to leave this world.
